    "The singularity occurs shortly thereafter.",
    "In summary, even if automation induces wages to collapse to the returns to capital at A, rapid technological progress from the automation of R&D allows workers to benet from the advancement of AI once sucient automation has taken place.",
    "More generally, the force described in this subsection is plausible, and sucient progress in AI will likely indeed lead to rapid technological advances and increases in living standards.",
